title: Episode 308: Don't make me call my Godfather (Feat. Sabrina Sidoti)
itunes:title: Episode 308: Don't make me call my Godfather (Feat. Sabrina Sidoti)
description:
Fitness Instructor & former pornstar, Sabrina Sidoti joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and takes us through her wild life story. Sabrina grew up in a mob family and her definition of "normal," is far from what the average human grew up in. Sabrina opens up about her run-ins with the law, covering for her father, the abuse she's faced from her ex, and much, much more. By the end of this episode...you'll be waiting for this to be a movie. Enjoy!
